<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcc69490a-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s47532"><num value="47532">§ 47532.</num><heading> Judicial review</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">An action taken by the Secretary of Transportation under any of sections 47528–47531 or 47534 of this title is subject to judicial review as provided under <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s46110">section 46110 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcc69490b-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1293">108 Stat. 1293</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/103/429/s6/74">Pub. L. 103–429, § 6(74)</ref>, <date date="1994-10-31">Oct. 31, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4388">108 Stat. 4388</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/112/95/tV/s506/b/2">Pub. L. 112–95, title V, § 506(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="2012-02-14">Feb. 14, 2012</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/126/106">126 Stat. 106</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
